movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: Ehh this movie is ok
review: This movie has a weird tone thanks to the awkward performances mixing with the grand world building, epic soundtrack, great action and a basic plot that drags on honestly if this movie was cut down to 90-100 minutes and maybe provided some motivation for the villains it'd be a 7-8 at least

movie_title: Star Wars: Episode IV - A New Hope
title: This movie is awesome
review:
From beginning to end it's a wonderful film.
The effects may look dated but that just adds extra charm for me.
My only complaint is the climax dragged on a little bit I can see they were trying to make it intense but I think it could've been trimmed down a bit

title: A really weird movie
review: This movie does offer alot of cool spectacle and it can be pretty funny but it's also nonsensical. Now I have no problem with a movie being odd but this just makes so little sense that it's more of a huh what? Kind of weird rather than a oh wow kind of weird.
